        <td width="100%" height="50" align="center" valign="middle" bgcolor="#fbb040" style="font-family:'Century Gothic', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size:22px; line-height:28px; color:#ffffff;"><strong>What you need to know and do before you start NCS</strong></td>
